    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everyone thinks a lot about what’s above us, but rarely about what’s beneath. A mysterious structure was found in the middle of the desert. Its entrance leads far below—into depths no one has ever recorded. <strong>This is the <i>Underworld</i>.</strong>  <br> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Wave-based coop roguelike</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight waves of monsters</strong> and move deeper into the <strong><i>Underworld</i></strong>. Waves get harder, and some are special. <strong>Find the boss</strong>, defeat it, and descend to the next layer. Each layer has its <strong>own enemies, environment, story, and boss</strong>. Pick your route, stack perks, and go deeper to discover what the <strong><i>Underworld</i></strong> hides.<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/ce83d88d266447ee2d9be449e1f40609.poster.avif?t=1764608837\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/ce83d88d266447ee2d9be449e1f40609.webm?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/ce83d88d266447ee2d9be449e1f40609.mp4?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Spend your points wisely</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each monster you kill gives you points. Spend them to <strong>open doors</strong>, <strong>buy perks and weapons</strong>, or <strong>try the Mystery Box</strong>. Doors change your route and how fast you reach shops, events, and the boss room. You can also <strong>save points and extract them into Undercoins</strong>, a permanent currency you use at the <strong>Tavern</strong>. In co-op, plan together: <strong>every point matters</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/219e67e7d1f2c577850267368f07b812.poster.avif?t=1764608837\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/219e67e7d1f2c577850267368f07b812.webm?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/219e67e7d1f2c577850267368f07b812.mp4?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Tavern</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>Tavern</strong> is your hub between runs. Here you rest, talk to NPCs, and spend <strong>Undercoins</strong> (your permanent money). You can turn run points into Undercoins at extract spots, then use them to unlock <strong>new weapons</strong>, <strong>perk levels</strong>, <strong>starting kits</strong>, and small <strong>boosts</strong> for your next run.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/14f989d3c901d1f720314d23509d6480.poster.avif?t=1764608837\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/14f989d3c901d1f720314d23509d6480.webm?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/14f989d3c901d1f720314d23509d6480.mp4?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Procedural generation</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every run is different. <strong><i>Underworld</i></strong> builds each <strong>level dynamically</strong>, mixing <strong>hand-made rooms</strong> with <strong>smart random rules</strong>. You will see familiar shapes, but the path, the fights, and the rewards <strong>change each time</strong>. <strong>You must adapt</strong> and prepare your team to pick up right upgrades for what the game throws at you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/d343db92c97ccf81c084479f8b78cd7c.poster.avif?t=1764608837\" aria-label=\"uwproceduralgenerationPreview\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/d343db92c97ccf81c084479f8b78cd7c.webm?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293950/extras/d343db92c97ccf81c084479f8b78cd7c.mp4?t=1764608837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
